#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/noise.rst:14
msgid ""
"*Noise* is an old feature. The :doc:`Displace Modifier </modeling/modifiers/"
"deform/displace>` is a non-destructive alternative to the Noise tool and is a "
"more flexible way to realize these sort of effects. The key advantages of the "
"modifier are that it can be canceled at any moment, you can precisely control "
"how much and in which direction the displacement is applied, and much more..."
msgstr ""
"*噪波* 是一个老工具。 :doc:`置换修改器 </modeling/modifiers/deform/displace>` "
"是噪波工具的非破坏版本，一种更加弹性的实现这类效果的方法。修改器最关键的优势在"
"于可以随时取消，可以精确控制置换的程度和方向等。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/noise.rst:20
msgid ""
"The *Noise* function allows you to displace vertices in a mesh based on the "
"gray values of the first texture slot of the material applied to the mesh."
msgstr ""
"*噪波* 功能用于使用网格材质的第一个纹理槽的灰度值来对网格上的顶点进行置换。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/noise.rst:23
msgid ""
"The mesh must have a material and a texture assigned to it for this tool to "
"work. To avoid having the texture affect the material's properties, it can be "
"disabled in the texture menu."
msgstr ""
"必须先对网格指定材质和纹理，该工具才能起作用。可以在纹理菜单中禁用，以避免该纹"
"理影响材质的属性。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/noise.rst:27
msgid "The *Noise* function displaces vertices along the object's ±Z-Axis only."
msgstr "*噪波* 功能仅沿物体的±Z轴方向置换顶点。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/noise.rst:29
msgid ""
"*Noise* permanently modifies your mesh according to the material texture. "
"Each click adds onto the current mesh. For a temporary effect, map the "
"texture to Displacement for a render-time effect. In *Object Mode* or *Edit "
"Mode*, your object will appear normal, but will render deformed."
msgstr ""
"*噪波* 会根据材质贴图永久修改网格。每一次点击都会累加影响。如果是为了临时效"
"果，可以映射该纹理为置换贴图，获得渲染效果。在 *物体模式* 或 *编辑模式* 下，物"
"体看起来是正常的，而渲染出来则是变形的。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/meshes/editing/transform/noise.rst:34
msgid ""
"The deformation can be controlled by modifying the *Mapping* panel and/or the "
"texture's own panel (e.g. *Clouds*, *Marble*, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"修改 *映射* 面板与/或纹理自身面板(如 *云絮*，*大理石纹* 等)，可以控制形变量。"

